    {
      "start": 13.561,
      "end": 164.777,
      "text": "See the image, feel the shock\nAssociate the pain with sin\nRewire circuits in your brain\nA new response will begin\nThe body learns what hurts it\nThe mind begins to change\nThese impulses can be redirected\nThough the process may feel strange\nAversion, conversion\nPain will guide you to the truth\nAversion, conversion \nBreaking patterns, making new\nThese feelings must be extinguished \nNo matter what it takes \nThe path to healing sometimes hurts \nBut your soul is what's at stake\nWhen you feel attraction \nPress the button, feel the sting \nYour body will remember \nThe lesson that we bring\nIce water, electric current\nWhatever breaks the spell\nThese methods may seem harsh to some\nBut they'll save your soul from hell\nIt's not cruel, it's necessary\nIt's not torture, it's a cure\nThe flesh must be subdued sometimes\nTo make the spirit pure\nSome call it inhumane\nBut what's truly inhumane\nIs letting you continue\nIn a life that brings such shame\nAversion, conversion\nPain has guided you to truth\nAversion, conversion\nBroken patterns, made anew\nThose feelings are extinguished\nNo matter what it took \nThe path to healing sometimes hurt\nBut your soul was what's at stake",
